schemas:    [security]
---

# underlying_quantity

---

The **underlying_total_exp_pool**  is the total exposure of the securitised pool.  Provided when underlying exposures are not known or attached to pool for securitisation calculations of w_ratio and Ka under sec_sa calculation approach.  Not required if underlying pool exposures are attached to the asset securitisation instrument and in order to determine the total exposure of defaulted exposures.  

Ref: OSFI Chapter 7 P126-128